- Any interpretation is my own viewpoint at the time of writing.
- I do not intend to defame, slander, or harm any person.
- I avoid real names and identifying details where possible, especially involving a minor.
- If any resemblance to real persons is inferred, it is incidental to recounting my personal experience.
- Where I reference public facts, I do so for context only.

